{"tid":838410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月7日(星期日) 超級颱風襲港討論區","createTime":"2018-09-27T05:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T04:18:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82d5dc69f865daa464fc26fc883b3103b08ad121","tid":838410,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1905775/org/a95cb26f34e2692042384cf63e44510d.jpg/XfJRE_vR7AhWSw_qxqt-aAajeX12A6PqktO1MJLTtTA?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1905775%2Forg%2Fa95cb26f34e2692042384cf63e44510d.jpg%2FXfJRE_vR7AhWSw_qxqt-aAajeX12A6PqktO1MJLTtTA%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=81190cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未命名颱風 將會成功達陣,穿過菲律賓台灣海<br />\n<br />\n美國全球預報系統（GFS）則預測，這個熱帶氣旋的形成時間會較ECMWF的預測更早，將在本月底時已經在關島附近形成，其時潭美正吹襲日本，這個潛在颱風其實會以跟潭美相似的路徑移動，即同樣會在中途「轉彎」向北移動吹向日本，如果成真，便令日本繼飛燕及潭美後，需要承受颱風來襲三連擊。"},{"pid":"5f716e6e96e0ae99a0b692136513e1ad34f3d558","tid":838410,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/135503_6ad74cac79810b08e7fa0f2fbb8cee70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F135503_6ad74cac79810b08e7fa0f2fbb8cee70.png&h=11fa989a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"287e90aff29d36e730ba1f7fd127867c9db02f1a","tid":838410,"uid":28743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be86a56dedd4b50ccd3db3cde91754374668fed9","tid":838410,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"星期日最近香港"},{"pid":"cb626e724ee8bb5ab38a141c3ec182ce7f840ff9","tid":838410,"uid":2